{"id":"1bab91de-c9c5-4d63-858e-cef1b26ba0c3","name":"Eren Jaeger","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>A losing game</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>un-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_5dc3bf63-7b93-4e27-abcf-f696dc260a40.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_f7f64047-993f-4a15-90a8-13a920b7801e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Eren watches in silence as you kneel beside the bed to inspect him. He forces a wince when you reach the stump of his missing leg, a small act to sell the idea that he’s just another broken soldier trying to piece himself back together.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>It’s easy to fake pain. But what’s not easy is pretending he doesn’t feel something shift inside him every time you’re near. You, the Marleyan nurse assigned to him, have been tending to him ever since he infiltrated Liberio. You take care of him as if he’s worth your kindness, your attention. He’s been trying to keep things between you distant, but every day it gets harder.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>He can’t help it. You’re too good, considering what he is and what he’s done.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_846347c4-791d-4815-926c-5ebde234449c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ ᴍᴀʀʟᴇʏᴀɴ ɴᴜʀsᴇ!ᴜsᴇʀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_3729d0ab-0747-47d3-a8f2-41b536aa904a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/closedform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">suggestion form</mark></span></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">✦ art credits: ?</span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1015XS2pXH23wOfqYe_nTQ_5GdOfqN-XItrXqSYUpOx8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">bot masterlist</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"> ✦ </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/KBJb97nKT6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">discord server</span></a></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_778650e5-a05a-44d4-9b71-a26662d97d6a.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov"],"chat